window.bookSummaryJSON = "Laura Lippman has claimed all the major prizes in mystery writing and is a <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author. <p>In this seventh novel from Lippman's acclaimed series, Baltimore investigator Tess Monaghan has her hands full with five murder cases that have gone cold. Each has a domestic violence angle, and the cases also share a disturbing connection - one that points to Tess herself.</p>"; 
